snippet.title: Just Cause: Mobile | Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Just Cause: Mobile for iOS and Android features some faces that will be familiar to fans of the franchise! As you start your journey as an agent, Rico Rodriguez & Annika Svensson will be among the mercenaries you’ll encounter, giving your player character missions and intel. 

Just Cause Mobile is a free-to-play action shooter set in the Just Cause universe featuring explosive single-player and multiplayer experiences. To learn more, visit our website and follow us on social media! 

Website: https://JustCauseMobile.com 
Facebook: https://Facebook.com/JustCauseMobile 
Twitter: https://Twitter.com/JustCauseMobile 

Check out the announcement trailer here: https://youtu.be/tdsn7YaX1OY
